```plantuml
@startuml duanfuxiang0_MysqlMigrationTool

actor User
participant "Main Program" as Main
participant "Canal (go-mysql)" as Canal
participant "RowEventHandler" as Handler
participant "BinlogParser" as Parser
participant "DAO Layer" as DAO
database "Source MySQL" as SourceDB
database "Target MySQL" as TargetDB

User -> Main: Start migration
Main -> Canal: Initialize canal with config
Main -> Handler: Register event handler
Main -> Canal: Start binlog streaming

Canal -> SourceDB: Connect to binlog
SourceDB --> Canal: Stream binlog events

Canal -> Handler: OnRow(event)
Handler -> Parser: ParseRowEvent(event)
Parser -> Handler: Return parsed data (structs)

alt Insert operation
    Handler -> DAO: InsertToNew(struct)
    DAO -> TargetDB: Execute INSERT
    TargetDB --> DAO: Result
    DAO --> Handler: Success/Failure
else Update operation
    Handler -> DAO: UpdateToNew(struct)
    DAO -> TargetDB: Execute UPDATE
    TargetDB --> DAO: Result
    DAO --> Handler: Success/Failure
else Delete operation
    Handler -> DAO: DeleteFromNew(struct)
    DAO -> TargetDB: Execute DELETE
    TargetDB --> DAO: Result
    DAO --> Handler: Success/Failure
end

Handler --> Canal: Ack event
Canal --> Main: Continue streaming

@enduml
```